name: The Golden Hour
description: The first & last hour of like light, just after dawn & right before sunset. The light makes everything feel warmer and softer. That is when we take a break & lets out a deep breath. The golden hour is not just the magic hour of photography , but for many it's the start of a new day or the end a crappy one. Right after dawn, right after sunset.That is when I love me the most. Sip a cup of tea, listen to my favourite track. All my worries fades way for a long second ergo my golden hour is my happy hour.
